## 公式

### FORM-001

- model_id: `MOD-001`
- expression_or_pseudocode: `resolve_weights uses explicit weights first; otherwise maps province through ALIASES and projects; missing province/weights raises ValueError.`
- evidence_refs: `EVID-WHKM-FORMULA-REGISTRY, EVID-WHKM-SEMANTIC-MANIFEST`

### FORM-002

- model_id: `MOD-001`
- expression_or_pseudocode: `score_performance: if rate<0.6 return min(0, -(0.6-rate)*300); if 0.6<=rate<=0.8 return 20+(rate-0.6)*200; if 0.8<rate<=1.5 return 60+(rate-0.8)*200; else return max(200,200+(rate-1.5)*400).`
- evidence_refs: `EVID-WHKM-FORMULA-REGISTRY, EVID-WHKM-SEMANTIC-MANIFEST`

### FORM-003

- model_id: `MOD-001`
- expression_or_pseudocode: `score_margin: if rate<0.1 return min(0,-(0.1-rate)*1000); if 0.1<=rate<=0.25 return (rate-0.1)*200; if 0.25<rate<=0.5 return 30+(rate-0.25)*200; else return max(80,80+(rate-0.5)*500).`
- evidence_refs: `EVID-WHKM-FORMULA-REGISTRY, EVID-WHKM-SEMANTIC-MANIFEST`

### FORM-004

- model_id: `MOD-001`
- expression_or_pseudocode: `score_settlement: days>60 -> -150; 20<=days<=60 -> min(100,100-(days-20)*5); 1<days<20 -> min(200,200-days*5); days==1 -> 200.`
- evidence_refs: `EVID-WHKM-FORMULA-REGISTRY, EVID-WHKM-SEMANTIC-MANIFEST`

### FORM-005

- model_id: `MOD-001`
- expression_or_pseudocode: `score_invoice: days>60 -> -200; 20<days<=60 -> min(0,-(days-20)*5); 5<days<=20 -> min(125,125-(days-5)*8); 1<days<=5 -> min(150,150-days*5); days==1 -> 150.`
- evidence_refs: `EVID-WHKM-FORMULA-REGISTRY, EVID-WHKM-SEMANTIC-MANIFEST`

### FORM-006

- model_id: `MOD-001`
- expression_or_pseudocode: `score_payback: days>60 -> min(-10,-10-(days-60)*2); 20<days<=60 -> min(150,150-(days-20)*4); 1<days<=20 -> min(200,200-days*2.5); days==1 -> 200.`
- evidence_refs: `EVID-WHKM-FORMULA-REGISTRY, EVID-WHKM-SEMANTIC-MANIFEST`

### FORM-007

- model_id: `MOD-001`
- expression_or_pseudocode: `score_audit_bias: if rate<=0.02 return min(120,120-rate*3000); if 0.02<=rate<=0.08 return min(60,60-(rate-0.02)*8000); if rate>0.08 return -420.`
- evidence_refs: `EVID-WHKM-FORMULA-REGISTRY, EVID-WHKM-SEMANTIC-MANIFEST`

### FORM-008

